library(ABTMSE)
loadABT()
#> ABT-MSE objects loaded
sfInit(parallel=TRUE,cpus=detectCores())   # initiate the cluster with two cpus
#> snowfall 1.84-6.1 initialized (using snow 0.4-2): parallel execution on 8 CPUs.
